blr.com/91910841273638b0317184d5985ae0f3/d6b25b8e2600708a-53/s75x75_c1/224c923ad6f1caeaebecde7853d30c56df0f839a.png 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/91910841273638b0317184d5985ae0f3/d6b25b8e2600708a-53/s100x200/2800118ee7366efe5de70a1469074a4f22a3c8e1.png 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/91910841273638b0317184d5985ae0f3/d6b25b8e2600708a-53/s250x400/6364bea6514d96b921ecfd3393f089d72cf7b607.png 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/91910841273638b0317184d5985ae0f3/d6b25b8e2600708a-53/s400x600/21ee9de49441627354ed8994e8898001e4494bb7.png 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/91910841273638b0317184d5985ae0f3/d6b25b8e2600708a-53/s500x750/99c5d59b50d382b3a77a5bd7d06c5bd5adabd26b.png 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/91910841273638b0317184d5985ae0f3/d6b25b8e2600708a-53/s540x810/3af1a984738a6a28148ef79ed832c16a5f606e2b.png 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/91910841273638b0317184d5985ae0f3/d6b25b8e2600708a-53/s640x960/682bcd36e058bc3a31fac91f7fae1151428e4a47.png 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/91910841273638b0317184d5985ae0f3/d6b25b8e2600708a-53/s1280x1920/e3cab56886360794a72d0c1cfa7e5d67e56f60c8.png 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/91910841273638b0317184d5985ae0f3/d6b25b8e2600708a-53/s2048x3072/0c0dda04f3bcb5b80eae23bf769bd7a18aa29764.png 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"/></figure></div><div class=\"npf_row\"><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"1824\" data-orig-width=\"2000\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/29ac3f076da4a23d0943868c0c762fe3/d6b25b8e2600708a-db/s640x960/b53e270036381148bccb1446e52ba2c0188cae02.png\" data-orig-height=\"1824\" data-orig-width=\"2000\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/29ac3f076da4a23d0943868c0c762fe3/d6b25b8e2600708a-db/s75x75_c1/18c4cb21ce9547c15bf3f263eee12856914c6eac.png 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/29ac3f076da4a23d0943868c0c762fe3/d6b25b8e2600708a-db/s100x200/37dabd2e4c90492f17c4727a38bc96b2238bff97.png 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/29ac3f076da4a23d0943868c0c762fe3/d6b25b8e2600708a-db/s250x400/1e23d001dd366499d64790f678e504ecaa3c2ebf.png 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/29ac3f076da4a23d0943868c0c762fe3/d6b25b8e2600708a-db/s400x600/e0a513f919740f679e264a7673a4c95575b6588c.png 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/29ac3f076da4a23d0943868c0c762fe3/d6b25b8e2600708a-db/s500x750/5e76586aa79ebbcbddab476660121e3c7efc9def.png 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/29ac3f076da4a23d0943868c0c762fe3/d6b25b8e2600708a-db/s540x810/fbefb5d9e64c8fcab04189cae954940fcd8df992.png 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/29ac3f076da4a23d0943868c0c762fe3/d6b25b8e2600708a-db/s640x960/b53e270036381148bccb1446e52ba2c0188cae02.png 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/29ac3f076da4a23d0943868c0c762fe3/d6b25b8e2600708a-db/s1280x1920/960afd6ed152597827861798c6491b9655e7e52d.png 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/29ac3f076da4a23d0943868c0c762fe3/d6b25b8e2600708a-db/s2048x3072/38a55664ea2cf2cf6097b8a4ce3785c6fde0c8d6.png 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"/></figure></div><p>My twin brother is the most important person in my life. He is a wonderful, kind person who (like me) often struggles with communication. But I never doubt that he loves me and he supports me. Where he struggles with stating feelings, he excels in gestures to show his love and support. On top of learning how to braid hair, he also did intricate research into fashion to help me develop my style, stood with me in the face of transphobia in the workplace, and buys me plushies when he knows that I&rsquo;m sad. I would not be where I am today without him.</p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"biblicallyaccuratemoth","active":true,"theme":{"header_full_width":686,"header_full_height":386,"avatar_shape":"circle","background_color":"#FFFFFF","body_font":"Helvetica Neue","header_bounds":"","header_image":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/0034ea4b30b8e7d6aba4d36d9c6cd417/780b9739770b7e4c-8f/s2048x901/1b4b241520c49e7aa5509612e2d8ff47dc299cf3.png","header_image_focused":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/0034ea4b30b8e7d6aba4d36d9c6cd41